 3 types of puzzle: Sudoku, Binary and Suguru.<br></li><li>Make use of the hint button<br></li><li>Maku use of the reset button to empy the board</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269710/extras/1f166ffb013f8851a8f80dfb197e9ce3.poster.avif?t=1676535436\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269710/extras/1f166ffb013f8851a8f80dfb197e9ce3.webm?t=1676535436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269710/extras/1f166ffb013f8851a8f80dfb197e9ce3.mp4?t=1676535436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
